</span></div><h2 id="cl_2">显卡兼容性</h2><p itemprop="description">以下是老鸽在详情页中给出的兼容参数</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a7858x7o/pic_28/' target='_blank'><img alt="抢不到RTX3080又想装机？风冷快乐盒XL兼容性先行体验报告" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202010/05/5f7b1bb4897813254.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a7858x7o/pic_29/' target='_blank'><img alt="抢不到RTX3080又想装机？风冷快乐盒XL兼容性先行体验报告" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202010/05/5f7b1bba29d248138.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a7858x7o/pic_30/' target='_blank'><img alt="抢不到RTX3080又想装机？风冷快乐盒XL兼容性先行体验报告" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202010/05/5f7b1bc1a6c433670.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">实际装机过程中，以R9 Nano（385px长x 280px高x 10px厚）为参考对象，装入机箱后在不安装顶部风扇的情况下，R9 nano最高处至机箱顶部留有130px空间</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a7858x7o/pic_31/' target='_blank'><img alt="抢不到RTX3080又想装机？风冷快乐盒XL兼容性先行体验报告" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202010/05/5f7b1bc559b256918.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">R9 nano尾部距离机箱内部前面板留有407.5px空间，结合R9 nano的尺寸，可以推算出显卡最极限尺寸在792.5px长x 409.99999999999994px高，高度为未安装顶部12015出风扇的情况，<strong>实测兼容数据基本与老鸽的差不多，算是比较极限了，大家选购硬件参考时千万不要再超出兼容参数啦。</strong></p><h2 id="cl_3">散热器兼容性</h2><p itemprop="description">根据老鸽的建议我原本准备使用<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/3385/" data-brandid="3385" target="_blank">乔思伯</a>CR1400，便宜又好用的130mm以内塔式散热，还带RGB灯效，找基友顺了个可惜得节后给我，只好拿出另一款135mm高度的利民AK120mini替代。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a7858x7o/pic_32/' target='_blank'><img alt="抢不到RTX3080又想装机？风冷快乐盒XL兼容性先行体验报告" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202010/05/5f7b1bc6e06884094.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a7858x7o/pic_33/' target='_blank'><img alt="抢不到RTX3080又想装机？风冷快乐盒XL兼容性先行体验报告" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202010/05/5f7b1bcf9902d3196.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">散热本体及配件全家福，支持AM4、LGA115x等主流CPU插槽类型</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a7858x7o/pic_34/' target='_blank'><img alt="抢不到RTX3080又想装机？风冷快乐盒XL兼容性先行体验报告" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202010/05/5f7b1bd42867d4089.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">TL-D12B PWM，非常规造型的300px风扇，配件附带了两组扣具，可惜这个风扇目前似乎还没单独出售</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a7858x7o/pic_35/' target='_blank'><img alt="抢不到RTX3080又想装机？风冷快乐盒XL兼容性先行体验报告" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202010/05/5f7b1bd3f276d7121.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">散热本体尺寸规格高135mm，5 x 6mm镀镍热管，单根热管理论解热能力55W，外观方面顶部最上层鳍片采用阳极黑化</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a7858x7o/pic_36/' target='_blank'><img alt="抢不到RTX3080又想装机？风冷快乐盒XL兼容性先行体验报告" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202010/05/5f7b1bdb37c069810.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a7858x7o/pic_37/' target='_blank'><img alt="抢不到RTX3080又想装机？风冷快乐盒XL兼容性先行体验报告" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202010/05/5f7b1be103ea52655.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">铜底镀镍镜面</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a7858x7o/pic_38/' target='_blank'><img alt="抢不到RTX3080又想装机？风冷快乐盒XL兼容性先行体验报告" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202010/05/5f7b1be15cfcc3443.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">果不其然，正常安装会和显卡冲突，此时需要用到老鸽在该机箱上设计的曲线救国方案</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a7858x7o/pic_39/' target='_blank'><img alt="抢不到RTX3080又想装机？风冷快乐盒XL兼容性先行体验报告" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202010/05/5f7b1be396aaa2247.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">当使用PCIE延长软线时可以调整转接线固定槽位</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a7858x7o/pic_40/' target='_blank'><img alt="抢不到RTX3080又想装机？风冷快乐盒XL兼容性先行体验报告" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202010/05/5f7b1beb502083227.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">使用内侧安装槽位时散热器仅支持130mm以内，此时显卡厚度可支持2.75槽</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a7858x7o/pic_41/' target='_blank'><img alt="抢不到RTX3080又想装机？风冷快乐盒XL兼容性先行体验报告" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202010/05/5f7b1bee28eda7404.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a7858x7o/pic_42/' target='_blank'><img alt="抢不到RTX3080又想装机？风冷快乐盒XL兼容性先行体验报告" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202010/05/5f7b1bedbfbfc9552.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">使用外侧安装槽位时散热器可支持到150mm，而此时显卡厚度必须是2槽内，且显卡IO挡板外侧不能有VGA、DVI视频输出接口</p>
